{"data": [{"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "0_1728803922.867231", "card_id": "Q_828901579", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 332}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待 Steam 商店页面明确出现警告：数字版游戏只是租赁，不是购买？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "据说和美国修正法律有关？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-a13fa96124fbe1eaa7938f2834fd0ed9_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "1028 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/828901579"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIgLHCiubEqLF2EAMaCTExMTA5ODI4NyDv+qe4BjAAOOEFQAByCTgyODkwMTU3OXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "1_1728803922.867706", "card_id": "Q_820211552", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 188}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待海康威视大规模人员缩编，「32 个研发区域只留 12 个，或波及上千员工」? 裁员原因是什么？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "有海康威视员工日前透露，公司近期正在进行大规模组织调整，32 个研发区域收缩到 12 个，「只保留几个核心区域，其余全部优化掉，预计会涉及 1000 多人。」对于此次调整，记者向海康威视方面求证，截至发稿，公司暂无回应。消息称海康威视大规模人员缩编 N+2 赔偿：32 个研发区域只留 12 个，预计波及上千员工"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-9a3bd235c58c832eab17a98a1742fa80_1440w.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "893 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/820211552"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIgLHCiubEqLF2EAMaCTExMTA4MzgxOSDmkaS4BjAAOPAGQAFyCTgyMDIxMTU1MngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "2_1728803922.868185", "card_id": "Q_848030141", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 63}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "马斯克星舰预计 10 月 13 日晚第五次试飞，或表演「筷子夹火箭」，难度有多大？此次发射有哪些看点？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "刚刚结束遭遇资本市场「恶评如潮」的 Robotaxi 发布会，马斯克又要马不停蹄地进行另一场科技大秀。 拿着监管刚刚打印出来的许可证，美国太空探索技术公司（SpaceX）周六通报称，「星舰」第五次试飞将按计划在 10 月 13 日举行。发射窗口将会在当地时间早晨 7 点开启，持续 30 分钟，也就是北京时间周日晚间的 20 点开始。 （来源：X） 发射时间表大幅提速 在本周之前，没有人意识到「星舰」第五次试飞会这么快进行。因为就在上个月，负责审批的美国联邦航空管理局（FAA）还曾表示，预计不会在 11 月底之前批准发射。 然而，SpaceX 在本周一突然发布声明称「有可能在周日进行发射」，这也被视为公司已经预见到能够「火速拿证」。 果不其然，就在发稿前 FAA 正式发布了「星舰」第五次试飞的许可证，还顺手批准了「星舰」第六次试飞的任务计划。FAA 确认，SpaceX 的「星舰」第五次试飞满足亚轨道测试飞行所需的所有安全、环境和许可要求。 （来源：FAA）火速获批今天就飞！马斯克星舰第五次试飞或将表演「筷子夹火箭」_ 腾讯新闻"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-7c2ea48cf3464db2e7cbec7204b4ca5f_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "298 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/848030141"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIgLHCiubEqLF2EAMaCTExMTExNjkyNyDPrqy4BjAAOLgBQAJyCTg0ODAzMDE0MXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "3_1728803922.869493", "card_id": "Q_839234929", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 137}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "广东 7 岁小孩每晚抱着电饭煲睡觉？你最离不开的阿贝贝是什么？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "阿贝贝可以冷门但不能邪门，怎么还有抱着电饭煲睡觉的？ 我现在睡觉还抱着奶奶缝的布娃娃。听说很多人成年后依然被阿贝贝支配，想看看大家的阿贝贝是什么？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-ef25c9d5b1dbe57542af9b610f05930b_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "285 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/839234929"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIgLHCiubEqLF2EAMaCTExMTEwODUyMSDS/6m4BjAAOIsCQANyCTgzOTIzNDkyOXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "4_1728803922.869943", "card_id": "Q_792045325", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.c